{
  "name": "sun-launch-best-practices-report-draft-8-9741fb",
  "title": "Best Practices in Hardware and Software Industry Product Launch Process \u2014 A Management Report for Sun Microsystems, Inc.",
  "description": "Aberdeen management report for Sun Microsystems (Aug 2002) benchmarking product launch processes. Interviews conducted June-July 2002 with 5 of 28 approached companies (Dell, IBM, Unisys, Computer Associates, Xerox \u2014 rest declined due to strategic sensitivity). Documents detailed lead times (beta testing 14d, configurator 30-45d, readiness review 90d/30d/7-14d/1-7d, pricing 60d guidelines/30-45d signoff, training 14d or 4-6 weeks, web site 30d) and delivery methods for launch materials.",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "created": "2026-04-19",
